@startuml bdd_state_dict
title <<bdd>> CRenderContext state{} dict schema
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor<<root>> #ffe0b2
    BorderColor<<root>> #e65100
    BackgroundColor<<enumeration>> #fff9c4
    BorderColor<<enumeration>> #f9a825
}
hide circle
hide empty methods
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
left to right direction

class state <<root>> {
    win : RcMode
    pd3d_device : LPDIRECT3DDEVICE8 | none
    color : COLORREF
    alpha : double
    bound_texture : CTexture* | none
    primitive_open : Kind | none
    psceneview : none (commented-out field)
}
class RcMode <<enumeration>> {
    pre_construct
    active
    destroyed
}
state "1" -- "1" RcMode : win
note bottom of state
    Half-migrated wrapper.
    D3D device held but only
    CreateVertexBuffer uses it.
    All rendering is OpenGL.
end note
@enduml
